title: A Praise Chorus
lastfmSummary: "A Praise Chorus" is a song by Jimmy Eat World. It was the fourth single released from the band's 2001 album Bleed American, which was later retitled Jimmy Eat World. With its carpe diem theme, the song has been described as a "celebration of adulthood". After the second stanza, seven songs become the "praise chorus" of the title.
